metadata.name: PEAPES #1
metadata.description: Welcome to PEAPES CLUB, a creative brainchild of ODDITIES LABS; is an original collection of 10,000 NFT's inspired by two great icons (the monkey Ape and the frog pepe), Each design was elaborated with dedication by hand and digitized as tokens in the Ethereum Blockchain ERC-721 chain, there is a variety of rarities in styles of professionals, hobbies, myths, divinities and celebrities. Collect and get the RAREEST PEAPES. Visit our website and social networks to inform you of our ideas and thus be able to help us make this a true PEAPES family club
